{"slug":"sirkuler-25-0168eng","reference":"Sirkuler_25_0168ENG","gazette":"Federal Register Vol. 90, No. 31","title":"Decisions on the scope of steel and aluminum products subject to additional duties in the US have been published","date":"16 Şubat 2025","bodyHtml":"<p>The Presidential Decrees regarding the additional taxes to be applied to steel and aluminum products and the HS code lists regarding the derivative products within the scope of the Decrees have been published.</p><p>The additional duties on steel (25%) and aluminum (10%), known as Section 232 Tariffs, were revised in 2025.</p><p>Trump, in his second term as president, signed executive orders imposing a 25 percent tariff on steel and aluminum imports, regardless of country.&nbsp;</p><p>With the Decisions published today, the HS codes for derivative products outside the main product group were announced.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration-line: underline;\">The main product group of steel subject to 25% additional tax is;</span></p><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"caption-side: bottom; border: none; outline: 0px !important;\"><tbody style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; outline: 0px !important;\"><tr style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; height: 14.4pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><td width=\"179\" nowrap=\"\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border: 1pt solid windowtext; width: 134pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.4pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">HS CODES</font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></p></td></tr><tr style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; height: 14.4pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><td width=\"69\" nowrap=\"\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid win